{"tid":403392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣布，女人考左牌都唔應該比佢地揸車","createTime":"2017-09-17T07:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T13:40:15.000Z","uid":57357,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad09444b1e882916a717d6542b427792e625e7f0","tid":403392,"uid":57357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:22:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啲女人揸車把口行先，嗌先過煞車<br />\n<br />\n我今個月搭巴士已經有五次個司機行錯路，全撚部，係全撚部都係女司機呀仆佢個街<br />\n<br />\n女人揸乜撚野巴士呀？你揸私家車唔撞都偷笑啦，淨係兜圈兜左九個字呀！去揸輕鐵啦仆街<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女人唔撚識揸車<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你又唔好一碌鳩打一船人，都有女人揸車叻既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97792313a6fc6ab5e50c5b2d6289a1dd2ce80c2b","tid":403392,"uid":57357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:25:27.000Z","msg":"咁快就有女人入黎比負皮"},{"pid":"4ef6b7f9b02b18d3b3af675bc7822f7b1e31d866","tid":403392,"uid":129810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:28:39.000Z","msg":"樓主今日先知？<br />\n女人根本唔應該揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ead08252447edbb86046ac6430ac477843beed","tid":403392,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:33:29.000Z","msg":"輕鐵都要自己渣<br />\n地鐵自動渣啱佢哋多啲"},{"pid":"dcac9853cff242961dfef9800639e05e80ffb66d","tid":403392,"uid":57357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:32:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輕鐵都要自己渣<br />\n地鐵自動渣啱佢哋多啲</blockquote><br />\n叫佢地番去自己玩thomsa火車頭啦"},{"pid":"b9fb8f5801e78188a89203341af7b496eed7cd3a","tid":403392,"uid":57357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輕鐵都要自己渣<br />\n地鐵自動渣啱佢哋多啲</blockquote><br />\n叫佢地番去自己玩thomsa火車頭啦"}]}